        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Bureau of International Labor Affairs Authorization Act of 2020</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes the Bureau of International Labor Affairs within the Department of Labor to support trade and labor affairs, including combating international child labor, forced labor, and human trafficking.</p>]]></text>
